2006-05-15  Benedict Verhegghe  <benedict.verhegghe@ugent.be>

	* formex.py (Formex.nodesAndElements): The equivalence operation is
	now repeated by default to remove any equivalent nodes left over by
	the first call.

2006-04-18  Benedict Verhegghe  <benedict.verhegghe@ugent.be>

	* draw.py (isPyFormex): now returns True if the first line contains
	'pyformex', even if it is not at the end.

	* formex.py (Formex.maxprop): new: returns highest property value

2005-12-12    <benedict.verhegghe@ugent.be>

	* canvas.py (TriadeActor): new: shows the global axes 
	(Canvas.redrawActors): new: redraws specified actors
	(Canvas.setLinewidth): new: sets linewidth for openGL drawing

	* draw.py (linewidth): new: sets linewidth for openGL drawing

2005-12-10    <benedict.verhegghe@ugent.be>

	* formex.py: moved from numarray to numpy
	(Formex.sort): now returns copy, leaves original Formex unchanged


